= Frequently Asked Questions


Q:: How to check if access set is global?
A:: Use IPAccess::Set#global method on an object.

Q:: I'm trying to figure out real object that caused an IPAccessDenied exception to happend. Should I rely on +originator+ or on +peer_ip.tag[:Originator]+?
A:: You should rely on +originator+ attriburte of an exception object.




